」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:23:02.000Z","msg":"中國自己整個習近平和平奬頒比黑驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d66ae68974829c45b9d9ea64f02f8329c89f189","tid":2207011,"uid":295699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:24:48.000Z","msg":"你咪去提名囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e453619bdbea3abcede6def048f2844b115738","tid":2207011,"uid":203491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾獎難少少，達爾文獎袋住先OK？"},{"pid":"d107bca59bc431449c74cdbf5a30dcaf56b07d12","tid":2207011,"uid":76432,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"fa3eaad705ea8ed575e020a335a7e53491491ac3","tid":2207011,"uid":363468,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"收左人工做番自己既工作, 都要羅獎咁有趣??"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:26:03.000Z","msg":"做返自己工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢哋最大問題就係雙重標準，自以為係判官可以用私刑「懲罰」示威者"},{"pid":"00cf797118cb0d252e776ab9ba7fe577ee269f94","tid":2207011,"uid":271894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9e453619bdbea3abcede6def048f2844b115738","tid":2207011,"uid":203491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾獎難少少，達爾文獎袋住先OK？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"狗進化到識用兩隻腳行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"c35b7160f10ce5a70171e5b3534d53c88739d330","tid":2207011,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Chriskwok10/status/1306611059755630593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FChriskwok10%2Fstatus%2F